      "description": "Any rocky coastline - Cornwall, Pembrokeshire, North Yorkshire coast - cheap field guides from the Field Studies Council With a proper ID guide rather than vague pointing, rockpooling becomes classification and discovery. Blennies, shore crabs, anemones, limpet varieties, topshells.",
