      "description": "Whatever they're currently absorbed in - a video game, a card game, a TikTok trend, a skill at school Reversing the teaching dynamic - and being a genuinely incompetent student of something your child is expert in - changes the relationship in real time. Children who teach a parent something they love become more confident and more communicative.",
