      "description": "Grief Café UK (network of informal drop-ins, free); Men's Sheds Association (peer social groups for men, 700+ sheds UK-wide) Men's Sheds are social spaces attached to a practical activity - woodwork, repairs, making things - where men talk because they're doing something else. The conversation that emerges around a shared task is completely different from anything prompted or facilitated.",
