      "description": "Bouldering walls in most UK cities - The Climbing Hangar (Liverpool, Edinburgh, Bristol), The Arch Climbing Wall (London). Walk-in sessions from £10 - 14. Bouldering requires no equipment, no booking, and no partner. You walk in, put on hire shoes, and try problems on a wall that goes 4 - 5 metres.",
