      "description": "Outdoor Swimming Society map - outdoorswimmingsociety.com. Hundreds of legal, safe spots across the UK. Most are free. The physiological response to immersion in cold water is immediate, measurable, and unlike anything else available without equipment or cost. The ten seconds of shock followed by the adaptation - and the feeling 20 minutes afterward - is a reference point for what the body is capable of.",
