      "description": "Any peak or long route near you - Pen y Fan (South Wales), Scafell Pike (Lake District), Ben Lomond (Scotland). Guidebooks from £8 - 12. A physically serious walk - one where you're properly tired for the last two miles - produces a kind of mental quiet that nothing sedentary achieves. The body working hard crowds out everything else.",
