      "description": "Most UK cities have a BJJ club - British Jiu-Jitsu Association finder. Trial sessions usually free or £10. BJJ is ground-based grappling that relies on technique over strength - which makes it one of the few martial arts that remains genuinely effective regardless of size or age. The first session is completely disorienting and absorbing in equal measure.",
