        "region": "nationwide"
      },
      "description": "Timebanking UK (timebanking.org) - national network of local time banks where an hour of your skill earns an hour of someone else's. Free to join. Timebanking is a local exchange network where an hour of carpentry is worth the same as an hour of gardening or language teaching. The system values skills that markets chronically underprice.",
      "why_it_works": "The people you meet through it are people you would never otherwise know. The currency is time, which turns out to be a different way of thinking about what you have.",
